      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以DependencyInjectionLayer是入口，它直接依赖DeviceFramework、FirebaseFramework、LicenseFramework这三个框架，还有PresentationLayer对吧？然后这些框架再统一依赖DomainLayer？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DependencyInjectionLayer",
        "DeviceFramework",
        "FirebaseFramework",
        "LicenseFramework",
        "PresentationLayer",
        "DomainLayer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个流向。PresentationLayer虽然是UI层，但我们也希望它通过依赖注入来管理，最终业务逻辑都下沉到DomainLayer。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PresentationLayer",
        "DependencyInjectionLayer",
        "DomainLayer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出顶层结构：DependencyInjectionLayer向下引出四条线，分别指向DeviceFramework、FirebaseFramework、LicenseFramework和PresentationLayer。然后这四个节点再各自连线到DomainLayer。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DependencyInjectionLayer",
        "DeviceFramework",
        "FirebaseFramework",
        "LicenseFramework",
        "PresentationLayer",
        "DomainLayer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我漏了一个点——MainLayer应该也要体现，它是整个应用的启动入口，不过它主要是被DependencyInjectionLayer依赖，还是反过来？让我想想...",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MainLayer",
        "DependencyInjectionLayer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "刚才我注意到代码里其实没有MainLayer的依赖关系，可能是之前的设计草稿？现在的结构是DependencyInjectionLayer作为最顶层，不需要再往上依赖MainLayer。如果MainLayer是入口，它应该在最上面调用DependencyInjectionLayer才对。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MainLayer",
        "DependencyInjectionLayer"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "你说得对，我搞混了。当前这个图聚焦在依赖注入的层级关系，MainLayer的调用关系可以另画一张。就按现在的结构：DependencyInjectionLayer统管四个下层模块，全部收敛到DomainLayer。",
      "elements_involved": [
